Introducing....
CAPA Web Explorer
 - web-based interface for capa  
 - allows you to upload an executable and view the results in a more user-friendly way
 - https://mandiant.github.io/capa/explorer/#/

 - How do we use it?
    # we are on windowz, analysing cryptbot.bin. We would like json
    - capa.bin -j -vv .\cryptbot.bin > cryptbot_vv.json
    - open https://mandiant.github.io/capa/explorer/#/
    - upload the json file
    - use filter options and global search box to find what you want